---

<Layout title="About">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">About Aero</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">Placeholder copy — to be refined.</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-[#1D1D1F]">
        The build, host, test, learn loop in one place.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#6B6F76]">
        Aero is where you publish prototypes to live URLs and run recorded user
        tests on them, with AI insights handed back to whoever (or whatever)
        built the prototype. This page is a placeholder while we write the full
        Aero story.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
